# This directory holds per-org OrgProfile JSON written by
# ``backend/scripts/enrich_org_profiles.py``. The script writes one
# file per (board, slug) and ONE meta file per board:
#
#     data/enriched/<board>/<slug>.json      # org profile (or status envelope)
#     data/enriched/<board>/_skip_list.json  # slugs to skip on hourly cron
#
# The opt-in ``BOARDS_USE_ENRICHED_PROFILES=1`` env var on the boards
# runtime makes the runner consult ``_skip_list.json`` at ``load_orgs()``
# time. Default 0 keeps behavior unchanged for existing operators.
#
# See ``scripts/enrich_org_profiles.py`` and the OrgProfile schema in
# its module docstring for the full shape.
